short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Detect AI-generated text using the AI Content Detector API

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension detects how much of a given text is written by AI. It also allows users to see their past entries into the application. A free API key is required to be provided by the user. More information is available in the extension and the screenshots.
